Start
Initialize ESP32
Initialize Keypad
Initialize LCD
Initialize Bluetooth
Initialize Servo
Loop
Read 4-digit PIN
If PIN is Correct
Generate Random 6-digit OTP
Send OTP via Bluetooth
Start 30-second Timer
Read OTP from User
If OTP is Correct AND Time < 30 Seconds
Rotate Servo to 90 Degrees
Display "Access Granted"
Log Success to Serial Monitor
Else
Display "Access Denied"
Log Failure to Serial Monitor
End If
Else
Display "Wrong PIN"
Log Failure to Serial Monitor
End If
Repeat
